                  "revisionId": 2757741,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Landing a critical hit will produce a single flower that despawns after 30 seconds. Landing multiple critical hits in a single hit (e.g. from weapons with Multishot ) will produce multiple flowers."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Peculiar Bloom",
                  "pageId": 1293280,
                  "revisionId": 2757741,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The position of the flower is based on where the enemy was shot, e.g. shooting an enemy's knee will produce a flower in that knee. The flowers grow from several fixed locations within the enemy, as opposed to growing from exactly where the enemy was hit."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Peculiar Bloom",
                  "pageId": 1293280,
                  "revisionId": 2757741,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The angle at which the flower is oriented depends on the angle at which the shot was fired."
                }
              },
              {
